    <item>
      <title>挪威海产品出口因鲑鱼养殖场问题遭遇史上最大跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/norway-seafood-exports-slump-most-ever-on-issues-at-salmon-farms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[挪威是全球最大的鲑鱼生产国，由于鲑鱼养殖场出现问题，导致该国海产品出口上个月出现创纪录的暴跌，产量下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/norway-seafood-exports-slump-most-ever-on-issues-at-salmon-farms</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 07:01:39 GMT</pubDate>
